name: aliens having fun
description:
aliens having fun

my inspiration for this piece originates from hearing in a few podcasts the former navy pilot cmdr. David  Fravor sharing how he and his colleagues encountered UFOs at sea in 2004 before those UFOs suddenly disappeared. 

what happened next? meet "aliens having fun", of how I imagine aliens gathered with their mysterious lights at the bottom of the ocean to simply have fun.

ps. for reference this is a sister piece of larger ed. OBJKT#488927.

original art by tomi with ai, creation day 2021-10-30

3840 × 2016px
